–—ظVarchive/external_nushell_repo_backup/nushell.github.io/blog/2021-12-28-nushell_0_42.mdظ@7e8a77b05a16fb58b99c6d57d1fd997db01152805c444ad847fa862177cc42a0³title: Nushell 0.42‘¬Nushell 0.42ع`



Nushell, or Nu for short, is a new shell that takes a modern, structured approach to your commandline. It works seamlessly with the data from your filesystem, operating system, and a growing number of file formats to make it easy to build powerful commandline pipelines.
Today, we're releasing 0.42 of Nu. This release is a bugfix release of 0.41.
’گگع—Title: title: Nushell 0.42
Path: Nushell 0.42
Content:




Nushell, or Nu for short, is a new shell that takes a modern, structured approach to your commandline. It works seamlessly with the data from your filesystem, operating system, and a growing number of file formats to make it easy to build powerful commandline pipelines.
Today, we're releasing 0.42 of Nu. This release is a bugfix release of 0.41.
—ظVarchive/external_nushell_repo_backup/nushell.github.io/blog/2021-12-28-nushell_0_42.mdظ@5971ca99a5cb386dc04041d24ab238d5baf14a63a1208d8063a62c5c71ed8423³title: Nushell 0.42‘¯Where to get itعكNu 0.42 is available as 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/releases/tag/0.42.0] pre-built binaries
 or from 
[link: https://crates.io/crates/nu] crates.io
. If you have Rust installed you can install it using 
``cargo install nu``
.
If you want all the goodies, you can install 
``cargo install nu --features=extra``
.
As part of this release, we also publish a set of plugins you can install and use with Nu. To install, use 
``cargo install nu_plugin_<plugin name>``
.
’گگعTitle: title: Nushell 0.42
Path: Where to get it
Content:
Nu 0.42 is available as 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/releases/tag/0.42.0] pre-built binaries
 or from 
[link: https://crates.io/crates/nu] crates.io
. If you have Rust installed you can install it using 
``cargo install nu``
.
If you want all the goodies, you can install 
``cargo install nu --features=extra``
.
As part of this release, we also publish a set of plugins you can install and use with Nu. To install, use 
``cargo install nu_plugin_<plugin name>``
.
